premise_source_doc_sentence: Players are also able to choose the appearance of their firefighting units based on the different appearances of firefighters in different parts of the world , but this does not change the overall experience of the game .
There are more than thirty missions , each featuring different challenges which must be met with a range of different tactics .
Players can also use a number of different support vehicles , including ambulances and ladder trucks , to help complete missions .
